<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>TravelMate 관리자 - 대시보드</title>
  {{>partials/head-assets}}
  <link href="/css/admin.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="page-body page-body-sans page-admin">
  {{>partials/header}}

  <main class="app-main admin-main">
    <div class="container-xxl">
      <div class="admin-page-shell">
        {{>partials/admin-sidebar}}

        <section class="admin-content">
          <div class="admin-breadcrumb">
            <span>홈</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">chevron_right</span>
            <span>대시보드</span>
          </div>

          <div class="admin-page-header">
            <div>
              <h1 class="admin-page-title">플랫폼 현황 요약</h1>
              <p class="admin-page-subtitle">관리자 시안의 핵심 지표와 최근 운영 흐름을 현재 프로젝트 템플릿 구조 안으로 옮긴 정적 화면입니다.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="admin-summary-note">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">monitoring</span>
              <span>더미 데이터 기준</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="admin-metric-grid">
            <article class="admin-metric-card">
              <div class="admin-metric-card__top">
                <div class="admin-metric-icon metric-icon-blue">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="admin-metric-label">총 사용자 수</span>
              <p class="admin-metric-value">125,400명</p>
            </article>

            <article class="admin-metric-card">
              <div class="admin-metric-card__top">
                <div class="admin-metric-icon metric-icon-emerald">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined">home_work</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="admin-metric-label">숙소 수</span>
              <p class="admin-metric-value">8,231개</p>
            </article>

            <article class="admin-metric-card">
              <div class="admin-metric-card__top">
                <div class="admin-metric-icon metric-icon-purple">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined">edit_note</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="admin-metric-label">오늘 신규 게시글</span>
              <p class="admin-metric-value">452개</p>
            </article>

            <article class="admin-metric-card">
              <div class="admin-metric-card__top">
                <div class="admin-metric-icon metric-icon-orange">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined">payments</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="admin-metric-label">금일 예약 매출</span>
              <p class="admin-metric-value">₩12.4M</p>
            </article>
          </div>

          <div class="admin-grid-2">
            <section class="admin-panel">
              <div class="admin-panel__header">
                <h2 class="admin-panel__title">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined">hotel</span>
                  <span>숙소 리스트</span>
                </h2>
                <a class="admin-link" href="#" onclick="return false;" aria-disabled="true">전체보기</a>
              </div>

              <div class="admin-table-wrap">
                <table class="table admin-table">
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                      <th>숙소명</th>
                      <th>지역</th>
                      <th class="text-center">상태</th>
                      <th class="text-end">등록일</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <td><p class="admin-name">제주 귤림 스테이</p></td>
                      <td>제주도</td>
                      <td class="text-center"><span class="admin-status-badge status-success">운영중</span></td>
                      <td class="text-end">2023.10.20</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td><p class="admin-name">강릉 바다향기 펜션</p></td>
                      <td>강원도</td>
                      <td class="text-center"><span class="admin-status-badge status-success">운영중</span></td>
                      <td class="text-end">2023.10.15</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td><p class="admin-name">경주 한옥 고택</p></td>
                      <td>경상북도</td>
                      <td class="text-center"><span class="admin-status-badge status-warning">점검중</span></td>
                      <td class="text-end">2023.09.28</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td><p class="admin-name">서울 남산 뷰 호텔</p></td>
                      <td>서울</td>
                      <td class="text-center"><span class="admin-status-badge status-success">운영중</span></td>
                      <td class="text-end">2023.09.12</td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section class="admin-panel">
              <div class="admin-panel__header">
                <h2 class="admin-panel__title">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined">forum</span>
                  <span>실시간 커뮤니티 게시글</span>
                </h2>
                <a class="admin-link" href="#" onclick="return false;" aria-disabled="true">전체보기</a>
              </div>

              <div class="admin-panel__body">
                <div class="admin-feed-list">
                  <article class="admin-feed-item">
                    <div class="admin-feed-icon">
                      <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-grow-1 min-w-0">
                      <p class="admin-feed-title">이번 주말 여수 밤바다 코스 추천 부탁드려요!</p>
                      <p class="admin-feed-meta">
                        <span>작성자: 김여행자</span>
                        <span>•</span>
                        <span>2분 전</span>
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined admin-feed-actions">more_vert</span>
                  </article>

                  <article class="admin-feed-item">
                    <div class="admin-feed-icon">
                      <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-grow-1 min-w-0">
                      <p class="admin-feed-title">가평 펜션 사기 주의하세요. 정보 공유합니다.</p>
                      <p class="admin-feed-meta">
                        <span>작성자: 정의로운발걸음</span>
                        <span>•</span>
                        <span>15분 전</span>
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined admin-feed-actions">more_vert</span>
                  </article>

                  <article class="admin-feed-item">
                    <div class="admin-feed-icon">
                      <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-grow-1 min-w-0">
                      <p class="admin-feed-title">혼자 제주도 한달살기 숙소 구했습니다!</p>
                      <p class="admin-feed-meta">
                        <span>작성자: 솔로투어</span>
                        <span>•</span>
                        <span>45분 전</span>
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined admin-feed-actions">more_vert</span>
                  </article>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  {{>partials/footer}}
  {{>partials/scripts}}
</body>
</html>
